{"tid":44052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘警署聖誕派對爆風化事件　警司涉攬腰掃背性騷擾多名女警","createTime":"2016-12-18T03:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T12:33:18.000Z","uid":48093,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c49d63c2d7df74873473d9aee0e59477d456175","tid":44052,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161218/s00001/1481993224380SL4_4853833614A35B8AAF94B31A856B93B7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161218%2Fs00001%2F1481993224380SL4_4853833614A35B8AAF94B31A856B93B7.jpg&h=e5b1b5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n觀塘警區上周三（14日）晚上於觀塘警署警官餐廳舉辦聖誕派對，《明報》其後接獲投訴，指一名助理指揮官（刑事）在派對的抽獎環節時，以「長腿」及「著超短裙」等形容在場女警，又談及「大波」字眼，並對女警作出「攬腰」及「掃背」等行為，同場男警上前阻止時，遭該警司揮拳回擊，其後該警司被帶離場。<br />\n<br />\n有在場人士向本報表示，涉事警司在派對上，不時走近女同袍，以「面貼面」的距離與對方傾談，並作出「攬腰」及「掃背」等行為，約5名女警涉事，有人被觸摸後「眼濕濕」。有目擊者指，有女警曾推開及避開他，亦有男警以身體分隔雙方，但該警司揮拳或拍打在場男女警，當時已有警務人員明言：「你唔好再打。」涉事警司其後再突然衝前拍打其中一名女警，最終被在場人士制止並帶離場。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨回應稱，暫未接獲相關投訴，但強調非常重視人員操守，如有人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行調查及紀律覆檢。本報曾致電涉事警司的辦公室電話，但無人接聽。"},{"pid":"eca334c208cf0b4cfc9e63d110aac3a032479adb","tid":44052,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:19:30.000Z","msg":"我冇做錯！"},{"pid":"f193b556436f91af6a4dc2bf27a823a87ba03c6c","tid":44052,"uid":21120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:19:34.000Z","msg":"拿！香港警察呢...."},{"pid":"ebb6224e03f7b9958b6aa2a62382d6ffe8877d0d","tid":44052,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646af565d5ddb316903d1e9420d2410998ba4a7b","tid":44052,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"有目擊者指，有女警曾推開及避開他，亦有男警以身體分隔雙方，但該警司揮拳或拍打在場男女警，當時已有警務人員明言：「你唔好再打。」涉事警司其後再突然衝前拍打其中一名女警，最終被在場人士制止並帶離場。<br />\n<br />\n原來有警察咁勇？<br />\n以下犯上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e65238ec5e7c9ac2752a095364154afb3f5d869","tid":44052,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"阿Sir抽水唔駛你教"},{"pid":"74bd6f859c9cbd4be53212b92f41d59f25091b64","tid":44052,"uid":37466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.lifelearn-cliented.com/cms/resources/body/7406/bite_wounds_in_dogs_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lifelearn-cliented.com%2Fcms%2Fresources%2Fbody%2F7406%2Fbite_wounds_in_dogs_3.jpg&h=cb9fb146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c3510146999e3b107b1f796814723eb8c79a315","tid":44052,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有目擊者指，有女警曾推開及避開他，亦有男警以身體分隔雙方，但該警司揮拳或拍打在場男女警，當時已有警務人員明言：「你唔好再打。」涉事警司其後再突然衝前拍打其中一名女警，最終被在場人士制止並帶離場。<br />\n<br />\n原來有警察咁勇？<br />\n以下犯上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條卒仔下場可能同施sir 一樣咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a424c73443640bd5517dc05fb9a59f08f73e7e46","tid":44052,"uid":44144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d2e3ec57e6509e23790822e5d18de3fcff3445","tid":44052,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓上咪貼左"},{"pid":"1c6958189e6a7a2f51c2c9d8fc69dc6bca329865","tid":44052,"uid":20248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"tb都岩?"},{"pid":"b0c305f8aadce316e9a9db00ff1e73b18